msgstr "Uvod"

#: index.docbook:30
msgid ""
"This module of the &kcontrol; gives you options for configuring the way in "
"which the &kdesu; program treats passwords. &kdesu; will ask you for a "
"password when you try to carry out some privileged actions, such as changing "
"the date/time stored in your system clock, or adding new users on your "
"computer."
msgstr ""
"Ta modul &kcontrol;-a vam prinaša možnosti za nastavitev, kako naj program "
"&kdesu; ravna z gesli. &kdesu; vas bo vprašal za geslo, ko boste hoteli "
"izvršiti katero od privilegiranih akcij, kot je na primer spreminjanje "
"datuma/časa shranjenega v sistemski uri, ali dodajanje novih uporabnikov na "
"vaš računalnik."

#: index.docbook:36
msgid ""
"Privileged actions such as those described above can only be carried out by "
"root or a user with administrator permissions on your system. You will need "
"to enter the password for the root account when you want to carry out such "
"actions."
msgstr ""
"Privilegirane akcije, kot so opisane zgoraj, se lahko vršijo samo od root "
"ali uporabnika z administratorskimi dovoljenji na vašem sistemu. Ko boste "
"hoteli izvršiti akcije takega tipa, boste morali vnesti root geslo."

#: index.docbook:41
msgid ""
"The options in this module do not affect the behavior of passwords in other "
"programs such as <application>KMail</application>."
msgstr ""
"Možnosti v tem modulu ne vplivajo na obnašanje gesel v programih kot je "
"<application>KMail</application>."

#: index.docbook:48
msgid "<title>Use</title>"
msgstr "<title>Uporaba</title>"

#: index.docbook:50
msgid ""
"There are two configuration options for passwords. The first is to control "
"the visual feedback that you receive when you type a password. The actual "
"characters in the password are never shown on the screen. You can choose to "
"have each character represented by a <token>*</token>"
" character. If you want to make it harder for someone who might be watching "
"your screen to figure out how many characters there are in the password, you "
"can choose to have each character in the password be represented by three "
"asterisks rather than just one. Still another option is not to have any "
"visual feedback at all, so nothing appears on the screen when you type a "
"password."
msgstr ""
"Za gesla sta dve nastavitveni možnosti. Prva je nadzor vizualnih učinkov, "
"ki jih dobite, ko vtipkate geslo. Dejanski znaki v geslu se nikoli ne "
"prikažejo na zaslonu. Lahko izbirate, da imate vsak znak predstavljen z "
"znakom <token>*</token>. Če želite nekomu zagosti, ki bi vam mogoče "
"gledal na vaš zaslon, da bi odkril koliko znakov vsebuje geslo, lahko "
"izberete, da se vsak znak v geslu predstavi s tremi zvezdicami namesto z "
"eno. Še vedno lahko uporabite možnost, da sploh nimate nobenih vizualnih "
"učinkov tako, da se na zaslonu ne pojavi ničesar, ko vtipkate geslo."

#: index.docbook:60
msgid ""
"If you work in a reasonably secure environment, you can check the option "
"labeled <guilabel>Remember Passwords</guilabel>, and then choose a time "
"period in minutes using the spinner labeled <guilabel>Timeout</guilabel>. "
"(You can either type a number between 5 and 1200 minutes, or use the arrows "
"on the spinner.)"
msgstr ""
"Če delate v zmerno varnem okolju, lahko izberete možnost z oznako "
"<guilabel>Zapomni si gesla</guilabel> in potem izberite časovni interval v "
"minutah z uporabo vrtilnega polja z oznako <guilabel>Zakasnitev</guilabel>. "
"(Lahko vnesete število med 5 in 1200 minitami, ali uporabite puščice "
"vrtilnega polja.)"

#: index.docbook:66
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Remember passwords</guilabel> option has been selected, "
"<application>kdesu</application> will not ask you for a password for the "
"length of time specified, after you have given the password once. Keep in "
"mind, however, that this makes your workstation less secure."
msgstr ""
"Če je bila izbrana možnost <guilabel>Zapomni si gesla</guilabel>, vas "
"<application>kdesu</application> ne bo vprašal za geslo toliko časa, kot "
"je bila določena zakasnitev, ko ste mu že enkrat vnesli geslo. Zavedajte "
"se, da to, kakorkoli že, naredi vašo delovno postajo manj varno."

#: index.docbook:71
msgid ""
"You should avoid selecting the <guilabel>Remember passwords</guilabel> "
"option if you are working in an insecure area, such as a publicly accessible "
"workstation. Also, note that choosing a shorter timeout may be better if you "
"are in a less secure environment."
msgstr ""
"Možnost <guilabel>Zapomni si gesla</guilabel> nebi smeli izbrati, če "
"delate na nevarnem področju, kot so javno dostopne delovne postaje. Vedite "
"tudi, da izbira krajšega intervala bi bila boljša, če delate v manj "
"varnem okolju."

